DOS15325	Darkness	Darkness	.[13][10]When you first start you will find yourself in a small area with 5 statues.[13][10]This is actually part of the copy protection. You must take the number at the[13][10]bottom of the screen, then use them with the included code sheet to determine[13][10]how many times to strike each statue.[13][10].[13][10]For example. If the number is 104-05-5, you would look up page 104, Row 5,[13][10]Column 5 This would give you the number 14222. So you would strike the left[13][10]most statue 1 time, the next statue 4 times, and the other three 2 times.[13][10].[13][10]Unfortunately the code sheet provided only has 6 pages transcribed of 20, so[13][10]you may have to restart a few times until you get one that is included. You[13][10]can do this by simply pressing ESC to drop back to the main menu and then[13][10]restarting.[13][10].[13][10]	C;;Darkness;|					call play	c:	Darkness	c:\Darkness call play|			Darkness		Yes	ece4230\dosbox.exe
